Boost Nine is "the supercar of Amazon FBA Software."  

Boost Nine provides you an easy way to check to see if a market on Amazon is a good or bad market to get into selling on Amazon through FBA with, and allows you to calculate your ROI, see related products, identify good keywords, and move forward with your Amazon FBA business!
